"title": "9122: eternity, and God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9122",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Whether one considers the past or the future, God alone is discovered to be permanent and lasting.</p>\n<h2>God's being, his wisdom and his word are eternal</h2>\n<h3>God has always existed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:4\">JOB 38:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:2\">PSA 90:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:12\">HAB 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1-John1:2\">JHN 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h3>The eternity of God's wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:22-Prov8:23\">PRO 8:22–8:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:14\">HEB 9:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:20\">1PE 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>God's word has always expressed his nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:89\">PSA 119:89</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:160\">PSA 119:160</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:35\">MAT 24:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23-1Pet1:25\">1PE 1:23–1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:8\">ISA 40:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's purpose to bless is eternal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9-2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:9–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3-Eph1:11\">EPH 1:3–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:2-Titus1:3\">TIT 1:2–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18-1Pet1:21\">1PE 1:18–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:8\">REV 13:8</a></p>\n<h2>Some aspects of the created order are eternal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:2\">MIC 6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:26\">GEN 49:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:15\">DEU 33:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:6\">HAB 3:6</a></p>\n<h2>Eternal life</h2>\n<h3>God bestows eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:11\">1JN 5:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a></p>\n<h3>Resurrection of the body</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:42-1Cor15:44\">1CO 15:42–15:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:50-1Cor15:56\">1CO 15:50–15:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:1-2Cor5:5\">2CO 5:1–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23\">1PE 1:23</a></p>\n<h2>God's eternal blessings</h2>\n<h3>His eternal salvation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:17\">ISA 45:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:9\">HEB 5:9</a></p>\n<h3>His eternal covenant</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:10\">ISA 54:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:40\">JER 32:40</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20\">HEB 13:20</a></p>\n<h3>His eternal glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17-2Cor4:18\">2CO 4:17–4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:10\">2TI 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>An eternal crown</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:25\">1CO 9:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:4\">1PE 5:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>An eternal inheritance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:15\">HEB 9:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></p>\n<h3>An eternal home</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:9\">LUK 16:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:2-John14:3\">JHN 14:2–14:3</a></p>\n<h2>The eternal kingdom of God</h2>\n<h3>God's eternal rule</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:17\">1TI 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:16\">PSA 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:10\">JER 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3\">REV 15:3</a></p>\n<h3>The Messiah's eternal kingdom</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6-Isa9:7\">ISA 9:6–9:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:32-Luke1:33\">LUK 1:32–1:33</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's eternal kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:11\">2PE 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:15\">REV 11:15</a></p>\n<h2>Eternal punishment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:46\">MAT 25:46</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41\">MAT 25:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:6-Jude1:7\">JUD 1:6–1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:13\">JUD 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:11\">REV 14:11</a></p>",
